descriptionHtml:
[b][center][size=3][color=green]
[font=Trebuchet MS][youtube]9PT3tIjq124[/youtube]
This mod brings Home Tree to Skyrim. This outdoor home has been built around a giant tree. Player can use this home for many different purposes. For example, there are lots of animals near the Home Tree, so the hunting should be easy and fun. Home Tree includes crafting table, enchanting table, tanning rack, smelter, blacksmith forge, mannequins, weapons racks, wood chopping block and much more.

[color=#6fa8dc]-Home Tree is located near the Whiterun's Wathtower-[/color][/font][/color][font=Trebuchet MS]
[/font][/size][font=Trebuchet MS]
[/font][/center]

[center][font=Trebuchet MS]Video and pictures will show more.[/font][/center]
[/b]
